title: ZINC - 0-DAY WEEK OF 2013 08 07 (NEW RELEASE COMIC PACK) [EARLY
description:
NEW RELEASE COMIC PACK FOR 2013.08.07 [EARLY EDITION]


LOOKING FOR MORE COMICS JUST TYPE ZINC OR HITLIST IN YOUR SEARCH BOX



Hi and welcome to the EARLY EDITION OF 2013.08.07 COMIC PACK, first off a thank you to those of you that have sent me feeback on my last torrent i done, its down to your feedback that i have created the EARLY EDITION.  There are a couple of pointers i want to clear up.

1.  This pack is INDEED comics that have SO far come out THIS week.

2.  There will be two packs, on the following Monday a second pack called LATE EDITION will up uploaded which will include comics release after the cut off point for EARLY EDITION and including EARLY EDITION.  

3.  Comic scans are treated the same as films, games and TV with groups racing to get out there scans first, so all scans are included which will result in dups but as they are by different groups i keep them in, up to you which you want to keep and delete.

4.  This pack is my own work I HAVE NOT taken anyone else pack and renamed or added my TAG too it, full credit goes to the scanners all i have done is given you a torrent so you can download in one go instead of lots of small torrents.

5.  More importantly optiflex given his blessing to carry on uploading the NEW RELEASE COMIC packs and of which i owe im a big thank you.

Once again i hope you enjoy and support this torrent has you have done so far with the NEW RELEASE and HITLIST, and lastly but not lest i big hello to the Wanderer......you know who you are keep it up....
